# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets — never commit (HF tokens, API keys, etc.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Data/secrets.toml
**/secrets.toml

# Environment files with credentials
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Canonical runtime data (root Data/, see Data/README.md)
# Ignore everything under the root Data/ except tracked scaffolding.
# Leading slash keeps this anchored to the repo root only.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/Data/**
!/Data/README.md
!/Data/config.toml.example
!/Data/**/.gitkeep

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Regenerable build output & dependencies  (the big offenders)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rust build output — any crate, any depth
**/target/
# Node / npm packages
**/node_modules/
# Python virtual environments (e.g. Data/tools/training-venv)
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/*-venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Orphaned / duplicate runtime dirs found in the tree
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The real workspace is ashkorix/ ; this root-level crates/ is a
# stale runtime leftover. Remove this line if you ever add a real
# crates/ workspace at the repo root.
/crates/
# The app writes a fresh Data/ next to wherever it launches from,
# creating drifted config.toml + ashkorix.db copies. Ignore those.
**/ashkorix-app/Data/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Model weights & large ML / runtime binaries
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.gguf
*.safetensors
*.onnx
*.pt
*.bin
*.dll
*.lib

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Databases (runtime).  If you ever need to track a seed/fixture
# DB, add e.g.  !fixtures/seed.db  below this block.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Caches & logs
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.cache/
# Catches build.log and rolling logs like ashkorix.log.2026-07-14
*.log*

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS / editor cruft
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/